Interface Grid<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the elements (Objects) that may be put in this grid
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGrid, Board, BoundedGrid
public interface Grid<E>

Grid provides an interface for a two-dimensional, grid-like environment containing arbitrary objects.

Version:
May 27, 2015
Author:
Alyce Brady, APCS Development Committee, Cay Horstmann, Anu Datar
